data.description: Welcome to 3116 Albans Place in the highly desirable Springhurst Community. As you enter the spacious foyer, you are immediately drawn to the great room a large, open space w/floor to ceiling windows and a massive stone fireplace to warm you on cool fall evenings. W/built-in bookcases and a vaulted ceiling, it's a perfect place for gatherings. The kitchen is large and has a center island and a breakfast nook & bay windows w/a wonderful view of the back yard. Formal dining room and formal living room adjacent to the kitchen. The primary bedroom has access to the deck, an ensuite with large walk-in closet. 2 additional BR and full bath complete the main level. The lower level has a large family room, a fireplace, a bedroom with full bath, an office, laundry area, extra storage two car garage, private patio overlooking the half acre lot.
